        <p class="lp-oecm-bar__copy">OECM Supplier Partner, Agreement 2025-470 &mdash; Ontario hospitals and long-term care facilities can purchase directly from Brant Business Interiors without an open tender or RFP process.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-oecm-bar__meta">
        <a href="/pages/oecm" class="bbi-btn bbi-btn--tertiary">
          <span class="label">Learn about OECM purchasing</span>
          <span class="arrow"> &#8594;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

